****"RENT TO OWN"*****

This Home is located in the Heron Bay Subdivision of Palm Bay.  Enjoy a very spacious 3 bedroom 2 bath with 2 car garage split floor plan, with Tile in Kitchen and wet areas, and Carpet in 2 spare bedrooms and Laminate flooring in master bedroom. Large screen enclosure with salt water pool to enjoy on those hot summer months. Includes Refrigerator, microwave, Washer and Dryer. Community includes club house, basketball court, community pool and playground. Close to major highways and stores. This home will go fast so act now. 

ALL OF OUR HOMES ARE "RENT TO OWN" AND NOT JUST STRAIGHT RENT.  PLEASE VISIT OUR SITE AND WATCH THE VIDEOS ON HOW OUR PROGRAM WORKS.  YOU CAN ALSO CALL FOR DETAILS.
